PHASE 4

The player who activated the secret phase reads the "Note to Judge", and becomes the Judge.
The two players with the most points become the two debatee's.

The Judge chooses a topic of their choice and provides the debatee's who two arguemnts. The debatee 
with the most points chooses the argument they would like to defend, the other debatee defends the opposite.

Any remaining players choose which side they would like to support.

The players will debate in the following procedure:

    Gavel
    The Pledge of Alegence
    1 minute team discussion (debatee's may talk to their gallery)
    Opening 30 seconds for each side
    Open debate for 3 minutes.
    Rebuttle 30 seconds each.
    Closing 1 minute monologe each.
    Judges Decison

Any deviation from this procedure = 1 drink. Ordered by the Judge.
If you do not address the judge as your honor = 1 drink.

A player may call an objection to an opposing players comment. If sustained by the Judge the opposing player drinks.
If the player is denied by the Judge, then that player must drink.s

The Judge may order any participant to drink, for disrupting the court.
    *If you disrupt 10 times you are held in contempt and must take a shot.

